{"type": "article", "id": 50733, "title": "前Givenchy创意总监接管Burberry，以及，水原希子担任Dior美妆亚洲大使 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-03-02T04:22:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 1831, "name": "复星"}, {"id": 43377, "name": "Chole"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180302115608IL0hRrp3eYzu8kas.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/burberry-taps-riccardo-tisci-chief-creative-officer-1202603025/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Burberry 任命 Riccardo Tisci 接任新创意总监</strong></a> | 昨日，Burberry 正式宣布， Riccardo Tisci 为品牌新创意总监，任命将于 3 月 12 日正式生效，同时 Christopher Baily 将于 3 月 31 日离任。Riccardo Tisci 在去年离开 Givenchy，现任 Burberry CEO Marco Gobbetti 也曾是 Givenchy 的 CEO，双方联系密切。 Marco Gobbetti 称，看中 Tisci 能够把街头时尚与奢侈品融合的能力。该消息一出，Burberry 当天股价一度飙升至 16.41 英镑。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-wolford-m-a-fosun-intl/chinas-fosun-to-take-control-of-austrian-lingerie-maker-wolford-idUSKCN1GD4PW\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>复星收购澳大利亚品牌 Wolford 多数股份</strong></a> | 日前，Wolford 方面承认，复星集团收购了品牌的大部分股份。Wolford 以紧身衣、内衣和衬衫出名，在一年前因为重组而陷入赤字。据路透社消息，这笔交易中复星斥资 3300 万欧元，收购了 50.9％ 的股份，另外还将提供多大 2200 万欧元作为增资计划的一部分。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-03-01/dior-kiko-mizuhara/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>水原希子成为 Dior 美妆首位亚洲形象大使 </strong></a>| 3 月1 日的记者会上，Dior 宣布正式起用日本女模特、明星水原希子为亚洲形象大使，代言 Dior 旗下的香水、护肤、彩妆系列产品。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>三宅一生推出了新香水，<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-03-01/isseymiyake-pure-nectar-de-parfum/topics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">L'EAU D'ISSEY PURE Nectar de Parfum</a>。 </p><p>这款香水主打花蜜香调，包括洋梨、玫瑰、蜂蜜的混合，它将于 3 月 14 日发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302114853aifcDq0yjIpbhUPd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302114849ZDOJEPo4SCA8del3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021148498X9fvulq37AQoSE2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>日本建材制造商田岛防水材料和牛仔生产商 Kaihara 合作，出了一款<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/572475\" rel=\"nofollow\">牛仔制的地砖</a>，它可以随使用时间而发生颜色变化，售价为每平方米 15000 日元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115118gVbOm8GWNiheLTaP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.591667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018030211511945SuRX83h01erWV6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115122pvx5BqI4kGS7Kusf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115119WSy9ULPRNVF7ZGCl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115121fVaNKlHi4zoJYcwb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.617251\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Supreme 太难买， Jonathan Graham 就做了个只卖 Supreme 的网站，叫 <a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/573934\" rel=\"nofollow\">Strictlypreme</a>。 </p><p>该网站允许所有的 Supreme 产品自由买卖，并由创始人团队会对 Supreme 进行专业的鉴定，每笔交易收取 5% 的手续费。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115000GMBgPxA4KLEHue6J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562225\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115006IhfGZt1yL8OX9w4J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562225\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>3 月 2 日至 11 日，<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/574084\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chanel</a> 为了宣传新产品 ROUGE COCO LIP BLUSH，在东京明治神宫前开设了快闪店，主题是“游戏中心”。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021151461ZPIKO2TAmX5zRiG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.664583\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115146w62Os1A8aqX9vngD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.664583\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021151520GCdMHErDg4tYaA8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.664583\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115146xN0yIneWlPSMJmQq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115146U7m8Esn3xYRA90Ol.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.099656\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-2018/paris/chloe/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chloé 2018 秋冬系列</a>，继续波西米亚式的浪漫风格。设计师 Ramsay-Levi 称，这是“展现一个女性性格的不同方面”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115233IoY7c85wq90s2iUC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115235qfFNrhQYXcGmu9Dg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115236L8odcFSTtrwElZ5y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115238rUgMAlb0s9CFt4J8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115239GwABxhfaz3qUijbg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115239p8wEuY5OvdZs9Hr3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115239B2t18Un5DsFriGYI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021152396exAYvXaWPjucZDs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021152410Unrh1ewCOd4YqG2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115242snbhi39cR8SoTY65.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021152420AVbST7IECX6rkHv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021152443XBvOkPs2aA89wnS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115245wxd3mCVfTe5Qz2W4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115245KBdGPJ1aAlTtu4mI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115245hi963LjYUNHZaDvP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021152468UNKDB05IaxFjPOZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115248yYDHM7pK3r2wmiza.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115248nSP0QkfIumBXWs1R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115249BMTtEWh5uwdyvj16.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115249RQMiJcoBuEWVGtzp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115250oAfGShW6EC7VUNgk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>最近备受关注的<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-2018/paris/lanvin/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Lanvin </a>发布了 2018 秋冬成衣系列。 </p><p>在之前麻烦不断的境地中，设计师 Olivier Lapidus 只有 40 天的时间准备这一系列，当中显示出了不少他本人对于技术的痴迷。（Olivier Lapidus 拥有 11 项技术专利，比如用光纤维制作的织物） 从秀场表现来看，不算太糟糕，但也没什么惊喜。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115317iwW0YOUA7vxo95N1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115318meS7FUA9QYW0DBtv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115318zgtUyhjGx5vRLw30.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115318RKZUp8kb6F2qg0LM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115319VZeOYW7ckX0u1GFr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021153195sOvjXYC2mzDWwpd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021153212RsU3pfq4kml6YEj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115323FLrjhSeJtHs963m2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115323S6fODWBmr43shJ1L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115324fst6OQ91GHnoxcRZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021153246K0puC2USGEO1z4M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115324MAoeErSb91kWJUYQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021153243gKtPNB69Ql8oYGU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803021153269GUp1NvM58bjBskA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115326rkjdGDi4PXE2IAxK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502930\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302115327fxYSXElpmK8ibqRD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Dior</p>"}